NBVEBIS.title: Broad Effective Exchange Rate for Venezuela (DISCONTINUED)
NBVEBIS.notes:
Nominal effective exchange rates are calculated as geometric weighted averages of bilateral exchange rates.

RBVEBIS.title: Real Broad Effective Exchange Rate for Venezuela (DISCONTINUED)
RBVEBIS.notes:
Real effective exchange rates are calculated as weighted averages of bilateral exchange rates adjusted by relative consumer prices.
